[@slide] Structure — flow & callout
[@subtitle] How a deck flows, end to end
[@note] Walk the flow left to right; dwell on Compile — that's the deterministic step. Press S to see these notes; arrows to move. [/@note]

[flow scale:2]
  [node icon:pencil title:Author] write the .sd [/node]
  [node icon:cog title:Compile focal] five stages [/node]
  [node icon:play title:Present] static html [/node]
[/flow]

[callout tone:tip align:center] Mark a node `focal` to make it the anchor. [/callout]

